"    </a>",
"    <br/>",
"    <a class=\"contributor contributor_credentials\" href=\"UTD.htm?3/56/3971/contributors\">",
"     Jerome D Waye, MD",
"    </a>",
"    <br/>",
"   </div>",
"   <div>",
